	"movq	%%mm0, %%mm2\n\t"

	"movq	%%mm1, %%mm3\n\t"

	"punpcklbw %%mm7, %%mm1\n\t"

	"punpckhbw %%mm7, %%mm2\n\t"

	"punpckhbw %%mm7, %%mm3\n\t"

	"paddusw %%mm1, %%mm0\n\t"

	"paddusw %%mm3, %%mm2\n\t"

	"psrlw	$1, %%mm0\n\t"

	"psrlw	$1, %%mm2\n\t"

	"packuswb  %%mm2, %%mm0\n\t"

	"movq	%%mm0, %0\n\t"

	:"=m"(*p)

	:"m"(*pix),

	 "m"(*(pix+line_size))

	:"memory");

  } while(--h);
